reviewText: Great add to the Sandler collection
Fun movie.  My girls love Jack and Jill!
The movie was unwrapped and just what I needed!:)
I received it quickly and was sold at a good price!

I love this movies. Adam Sandler is a great actor. I got this dvd because it came with 3 movies in one case.  There each good and I think there funny. I would recomend this. Its hard to explain the description of each movie in a summary. lol  But  if you have not seen these movies and your not sure you would like them, maybe rent them first and see if you like them.( but im sure you will)  :)
How can you go wrong with Adam Sandler
Just go with it is timeless!!
Bought it to see Just Go With It which ended up being the bad movie and Jack and Jill ended up being the good movie.  But three movies for $7 is a deal.
